==Korean==

===Interogative pronoun===
'''뭐''' ''mweo''
(abbreviation of [[무엇]] mu'eot)
# [[what]] - used in questions
#: 이게 '''뭐'''예요? (''Ige mweo-yeyo?'') '''What''' is this?
#: '''뭐'''라고 했어요? (''mwo-rago haesseoyo?'') '''''What''' did [you] say?'' 
